name: Alphabet - Italic Font
description:
Available in 26 characters in the colors Black or Radiant. 
Typed in Italic.

Radiant is produces mirror-like reflections and shines in every color of the rainbow. The gradient color changes depend on the viewing angle.

Comes in a black jewelry box.

Material: Sterling Silver + Acrylic glass

Chain length: 50 cm,  fastens with a spring clasp.

Also available without necklace.

name: Totepack White
description:
Heavy canvas totepack. 

This bag can be used as a tote bag, 
the long shoulder straps make it easy to wear it as a backpack. 
No more hassle when you go cycling! 

Made from heavy canvas, it fits most of your daily stuff, including a laptop. 
The zipper ensures that the content of your bag does not get lost during a night out or day at a festival. 

Practical for day and night, available in white.

100% cotton, YKK metal zipper closure.

Size: W36 X H42 cm.
